    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847810/extras/back_thumb2.PNG?t=1665254696\" /></span><br><br><strong>Tkium Exclusion Area is a short horror escape game which takes place in an asylum.</strong><br>It has been evacuated, and no one seems to know why...<br>You need to get out of this place, and quickly. Your sanity decreases slowly as you try to find an exit in this place that you may mistake for a nightmare.<br>Each corner hides a dark secret, and the story behind this place holds much more. Why were you here? What happened while you were asleep?..<br><br><strong>This game is a one-story game, which means there is only one storyline and restarting it will not change any of the objects.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847810/extras/back_thumb.PNG?t=1665254696\" /></span><br><br><strong>The area is fully locked down due to unknown incidents.</strong><br>Find ways to open each door, and escape as quickly as possible.<br>Be aware of your insanity: it can lead to your death. You need to get out of this place before the counter reaches 100%.<br>The timer shows how long you have been in here.",
